---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Rehabilitation Services | Medical Care and Rehabilitation"
  description="Comprehensive guide to rehabilitation services available to UK veterans through the Armed Forces Compensation Scheme. Learn about physiotherapy, occupational therapy, and vocational rehabilitation programmes.">
  <div class="container my-5">
    <h1 class="display-4 mb-4">Rehabilitation Services for Veterans</h1>
    <div class="row g-4">
      <div class="col-lg-8">
        <p class="lead">The Armed Forces Compensation Scheme (AFCS) provides comprehensive rehabilitation services to support veterans in their recovery and help them regain independence. This page outlines the various rehabilitation programmes and services available to aid your journey to recovery and reintegration.</p>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Physiotherapy</h2>
        <p>Our physiotherapy services aim to restore movement and function:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Personalised treatment plans for physical injuries and conditions</li>
          <li>Manual therapy techniques, including joint mobilisation and soft tissue manipulation</li>
          <li>Therapeutic exercise programmes to improve strength, flexibility, and mobility</li>
          <li>Electrotherapy treatments (e.g., TENS, ultrasound) for pain management</li>
          <li>Hydrotherapy and aquatic exercise programmes</li>
          <li>Gait analysis and retraining for mobility issues</li>
          <li>Vestibular rehabilitation for balance disorders</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Occupational Therapy</h2>
        <p>Occupational therapy helps veterans adapt to daily life:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Comprehensive assessment of daily living skills and needs</li>
          <li>Recommendations and training for adaptive equipment use</li>
          <li>Home and workplace modifications to enhance independence</li>
          <li>Strategies for energy conservation and fatigue management</li>
          <li>Cognitive rehabilitation for memory and executive function improvement</li>
          <li>Hand therapy and fine motor skill development</li>
          <li>Community reintegration support and skills training</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Speech and Language Therapy</h2>
        <p>For veterans with communication or swallowing difficulties:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Assessment and treatment of speech and language disorders</li>
          <li>Swallowing therapy for dysphagia</li>
          <li>Voice therapy for vocal cord injuries or disorders</li>
          <li>Cognitive-communication therapy for brain injury-related issues</li>
          <li>Augmentative and alternative communication (AAC) device training</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Psychological Rehabilitation</h2>
        <p>Addressing the psychological aspects of recovery:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Cognitive behavioural therapy for adjustment to injury or illness</li>
          <li>Stress management and resilience-building techniques</li>
          <li>Confidence-building exercises and self-efficacy training</li>
          <li>Group therapy sessions for peer support</li>
          <li>Family counselling to support the rehabilitation process</li>
          <li>Mindfulness and relaxation techniques for pain and stress management</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Vocational Rehabilitation</h2>
        <p>Supporting veterans in returning to work or finding new career paths:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Comprehensive work capacity assessments</li>
          <li>Job-specific rehabilitation programmes</li>
          <li>Workplace ergonomic assessments and modifications</li>
          <li>Vocational counselling and career planning</li>
          <li>Work hardening and conditioning programmes</li>
          <li>Liaison with employers for supported return-to-work plans</li>
          <li>Retraining opportunities for new careers</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Assistive Technology Services</h2>
        <p>Utilising technology to enhance independence:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Assessment for appropriate assistive devices</li>
          <li>Training in the use of adaptive computer technologies</li>
          <li>Provision of communication devices and software</li>
          <li>Smart home technology integration for increased independence</li>
          <li>Mobility device selection and training (e.g., wheelchairs, scooters)</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Rehabilitation Programmes</h2>
        <p>Structured programmes for comprehensive rehabilitation:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Inpatient rehabilitation for complex or severe injuries</li>
          <li>Day rehabilitation programmes for ongoing support</li>
          <li>Community-based rehabilitation services</li>
          <li>Tele-rehabilitation options for remote access to services</li>
          <li>Sport and exercise rehabilitation programmes</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <div class="card bg-light mb-4">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="h5">Related Services</h3>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
              <li><a href="/medical/specialist-treatments" class="text-decoration-none">Specialist Treatments</a></li>
              <li><a href="/medical/mental-health-care" class="text-decoration-none">Mental Health Care</a></li>
              <li><a href="/support/career-transition" class="text-decoration-none">Career Transition Support</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card mb-4">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="h5">Rehabilitation Assessment</h3>
            <p>Book a comprehensive rehabilitation assessment to create a personalised recovery plan.</p>
            <a href="/rehab-assessment" class="btn btn-primary">Book Assessment</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="h5">Rehabilitation Centres</h3>
            <p>Find AFCS-approved rehabilitation centres in your area.</p>
            <a href="/rehab-centres" class="btn btn-secondary">Find Centres</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
